# Modules Directory

This directory contains reusable NetMX modules.

## Structure

Each module is a self-contained 4-layer project:

```
modules/
├── ModuleName/
│   ├── ModuleName.sln
│   ├── ModuleName.Core/              (Domain entities)
│   ├── ModuleName.Contracts/         (DTOs, interfaces)
│   ├── ModuleName.Application/       (Services)
│   └── ModuleName.Web/               (Controllers, views)
```

## Adding Modules

```bash
# Add pre-built module
netmx add module Identity

# Create new module
netmx create module YourModule
```

## Available Modules

**Free Modules**:
- Identity - User authentication
- Authorization - Permissions, roles
- Audit - Audit logging
- Settings - Application settings

**Paid Modules** ($149-$299):
- MultiTenancy - Tenant isolation
- BackgroundJobs - Job scheduling
- Email - Email templates
- CMS - Content management
- BLOB Storage - File storage

See [modules catalog](https://netmx.dev/modules) for complete list.
